536
00:34:41,579 --> 00:34:43,376
- Amy, we have no choice.
- You know that!

537
00:34:43,481 --> 00:34:45,244
You have to go down
and help lift him on!

538
00:34:45,383 --> 00:34:46,372
No.

539
00:34:47,819 --> 00:34:50,014
- We have to tell them.
- Tell who?

540
00:34:50,121 --> 00:34:53,887
