543
00:34:56,794 --> 00:34:58,762
No, we have to try, Jeff.

544
00:35:01,466 --> 00:35:03,434
Amy. Amy! Amy!

545
00:35:04,469 --> 00:35:05,493
Amy!

546
00:35:20,384 --> 00:35:21,442
Amy.

547
00:35:22,053 --> 00:35:23,611
Amy! Ame.

548
00:35:27,024 --> 00:35:28,787
Help us, please.

549
00:35:29,827 --> 00:35:31,852
