Okay.

596
00:39:24,095 --> 00:39:26,563
- His hips.
- Are you sure?

597
00:39:26,664 --> 00:39:29,690
If you lift him at the feet
he's gonna bend at the waist.

598
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:33,861
Yeah, but I lift him here from his hips,
it's gonna arch his back.

599
