His knees.

600
00:39:41,746 --> 00:39:43,737
Okay, quickly. On three, okay?

601
00:39:43,848 --> 00:39:45,873
One, two, three!

602
00:39:45,983 --> 00:39:47,644
Oh, my! Oh, my God!

603
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,251
Just get him on!

604
